# Claude Commands

Pre-defined command files live in `.claude/commands/`. When a user asks about a development task (testing, formatting, linting, building, syncing, etc.), read the corresponding command file at `.claude/commands/<command-name>.md` for instructions. See AGENTS.md for the full development workflow reference.
